## Implemented Algorithms

### Supervised Approaches

- Random Forest
- SVM
- Deep Neural Network

### Unsupervised Approaches

#### Non-parametric

- SR
- Threshold
- Quantile
- Kâ€‹-Sigma

#### Statistic-based

- SPOT
- DSPOT
- Autoregression
- ESD
- S-ESD
- S-H-ESD

#### Machine learning-based

- LOF
- Isolation Forest
- OCSVM

#### Deep-based

- Autoencoder
- RNN Autoencoder
- Donut

